</em>, for folding, or even with you, for gloating, but they won=E2=80=99t =
accuse you of fraud. They won=E2=80=99t call the police, or even stop playi=
ng with you. They are part of a social context in which they expect their c=
ounterparties to try to deceive them, and in which they sometimes try to de=
ceive their counterparties, and their reaction to a bold and successful blu=
ff will mostly be =E2=80=9Cwow, good one, you got me.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is not true of most areas of life, but it is sort=
