=99s just the sort of patter they expect from a visionary tech founder; the=
y didn=E2=80=99t take that too seriously.=E2=80=9D That might all be sort o=
f true, but a prosecutor is going to be like =E2=80=9Cbut you sold securiti=
es by lying about material facts, no?=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px =
0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24908435.25929=
5/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMS8wOC8zMC90ZWNobm9sb2d5L3RyaWFsLWVsa=
XphYmV0aC1ob2xtZXMtdGhlcmFub3MuaHRtbA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa8aedfee" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-=
decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color:=
 #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Anyway</a>:<=
/p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After four years, repeated dela=
ys and the birth of her baby, Elizabeth Holmes, the founder of the blood te=
sting start-up Theranos, is set to stand trial for fraud, capping a saga of=
 Silicon Valley hubris, ambition and deception.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">Jury selection begins on Tuesday in federal court in San Jose, Calif.,=
 followed by opening arguments next week. Ms. Holmes, whose trial is expect=
ed to last three to four months, is battling 12 counts of fraud and conspir=
acy to commit wire fraud over false claims she made about Theranos=E2=80=99=
s blood tests and business.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In 2018, the De=
partment of Justice indicted both her and her business partner and onetime =
boyfriend, Ramesh Balwani, known as Sunny, with the charges. Mr. Balwani=E2=
=80=99s trial will begin early next year. Both have pleaded not guilty.</p>=
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ms. Holmes=E2=80=99s case has been held up as =
a parable of Silicon Valley=E2=80=99s swashbuckling =E2=80=9Cfake it till y=
ou make it=E2=80=9D culture, which has helped propel the region=E2=80=99s s=
tart-ups to unfathomable riches and economic power. That same spirit has al=
so allowed grifters and unethical hustlers to flourish, often with little c=
onsequence, raising questions about Silicon Valley=E2=80=99s tightening gri=
p on society.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another problem =
with this defense is that I suspect that juries also don=E2=80=99t want to =
hear it, though I suppose it depends on the jury. If fraud depends on local=
 social expectations, you want a jury that is in on those expectations. If =
you are a tech founder and get a true jury of your peers =E2=80=94=C2=A0a j=
ury of tech founders and venture capitalists =E2=80=94=C2=A0I guess it=E2=
=80=99s fine? <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2490=
8435.259295/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDg=
tMzAvdGhlcmFub3MtZm91bmRlci1zLWRyZWFtLWp1cnktd291bGQtYmUtc2lsaWNvbi12YWxsZX=
ktc2F2dnk/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB018326c7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemsco=
pe=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> I mean</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">Legal experts say what Holmes needs are jurors well-versed=
 in the startup scene who will be open to the idea that the blood-testing c=
ompany was an innocent failure rather than a massive fraud.=C2=A0</p><p sty=
le=3D"margin: 16px 0;">According to this view, Holmes may be able to prevai=
l if her account of the collapse of Theranos resonates with jurors=E2=80=99=
 understanding of how entrepreneurs make sales pitches to attract investors=
 -- and how best-laid plans can go awry.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin=
: 16px 0;">Sure, why not. If those bond traders had gotten juries of bond t=
raders they probably would have been acquitted.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">One more problem with this defense, for Holmes, is that she was pitchi=
ng blood-testing technology that apparently didn=E2=80=99t work. This allow=
ed her to raise a lot of money from investors, but also Theranos <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24908435.259295/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDYtMTgvdGhlcmFub3MtZGl=
kbi10LWp1c3QtaGFybS1pbnZlc3RvcnM/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0e680e2f" itempro=
p=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> did a lot of blo=
od tests</a>? That didn=E2=80=99t work? And patients who got bad blood-test=
 results will be allowed to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/24908435.259295/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9mb3JtZXItd=
GhlcmFub3MtcGF0aWVudHMtY2FuLXRlc3RpZnktYXQtZWxpemFiZXRoLWhvbG1lcy10cmlhbC1q=
dWRnZS1ydWxlcy0xMTYyODEwMzM1Ng/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa55c3b45" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">testify at her tri=
al</a>? (A trial about whether she lied to investors!) Even if the jury is =
like =E2=80=9Cwell sure she lied to investors but they were cool with that,=
 they like to be lied to, no fraud,=E2=80=9D it is harder to conclude that =
about the patients. If you go in for a blood test you expect it to work! Yo=
u didn=E2=80=99t sign up for =E2=80=9CSilicon Valley=E2=80=99s swashbucklin=
g =E2=80=98fake it till you make it=E2=80=99 culture.=E2=80=9D Venture capi=
talists backing a founder want a high-variance lottery ticket. People getti=
ng a blood test want a low-variance blood test.</p>
